Paper: hep-th/9903075

Date: 1999-03-09

Title: Soliton formulation by Moyal algebra

Authors: Takao Koikawa

Comments: 9 pages

Journal-ref: Prog.Theor.Phys. 102 (1999) 29-35

We formulate the soliton equations on the lattice in terms of the reducedMoyal algebra which includes one parameter. The vanishing limit of theparameter leads to the continuous soliton equations.